

================================

CLi editing shortcuts

================================

ctrl-b		move the cursor left
ctrl-f 		move the cursor right
ctrl-p		view the previous command
ctrl-n		view the next command
ctrl-a		move to start
ctrl-e		move to end
ctrl-w		erase preceding word
ctrl-u		erase cursor to beginging of line 
ctrl-k		erase cursor to end of line
ctrl-y 		paste erased text


